{"tid":514557,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"古代強制婚姻，單身者重稅","createTime":"2017-12-30T16:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T06:49:54.000Z","uid":149978,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9202ac83f955517c41c86b9dbec53c1e37458e4a","tid":514557,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://history.people.com.cn/n/2012/1116/c198445-19605668.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhistory.people.com.cn%2Fn%2F2012%2F1116%2Fc198445-19605668.html&d=iDzVAHoAp7BrWJAoeKcibYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=e7c018ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://history.people.com.cn/n/2012/1116/c198445-19605668.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ifeng.com/history/zhongguogudaishi/detail_2013_12/01/31706010_0.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ifeng.com%2Fhistory%2Fzhongguogudaishi%2Fdetail_2013_12%2F01%2F31706010_0.shtml&d=iDzVAHoAp7BrWJAoeKcibYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=e283f529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ifeng.com/history/zhongguogudaishi/detail_2013_12/01/31706010_0.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://culture.people.com.cn/BIG5/n/2012/1112/c172318-19552937.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fculture.people.com.cn%2FBIG5%2Fn%2F2012%2F1112%2Fc172318-19552937.html&d=iDzVAHoAp7BrWJAoeKcibYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=b8123910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://culture.people.com.cn/BIG5/n/2012/1112/c172318-19552937.html</a><br />\n<br />\n現代有強制教育，古代有強制婚姻<br />\n<br />\n亦試過不婚者，要交很重的單身稅<br />\n<br />\n為解決人口出生和男子婚配問題，有不少朝代採取強制男性結婚和女性出嫁的手段。<br />\n<br />\n古代曾經嚴懲「剩男剩女」<br />\n<br />\n在南北朝，過左法定結婚年齡，唔結婚，即犯法。最嚴格，曾經試過「女子15歲不嫁 家人坐牢」<br />\n<br />\n在漢朝， 《漢書&middot;惠帝紀》中就明文記載：「女子年十五以上至三十不嫁，五算 。」「五算」就是罰她繳納五倍的賦稅。<br />\n<br />\n在晉代，女子到了一定年齡必須嫁人，否則官府要強行給她找對象。"},{"pid":"7a772053cfdba08d3b2f7cc6a19a4d864c5f3622","tid":514557,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"